      <prop type="x-translation-ref">史記·《殷本紀》 1</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>殷契，母曰簡狄，有娀氏之女，為帝嚳次妃。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Qi of Yin's mother was Jian Di, who was one of the daughters of Yousong and the secondary wife of Emperor Ku.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
