      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">史記·《殷本紀》 2</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">史記·《殷本紀》 2</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>三人行浴，見玄鳥墮其卵，簡狄取吞之，因孕生契。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>She was going with her two sisters to bathe, when she saw a dark bird drop its egg.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
