      <prop type="x-translation-ref">史記·《殷本紀》 3</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>契長而佐禹治水有功。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Jian Di picked it up, and swallowed it, and thus being with child gave birth to Qi.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
