      <prop type="x-translation-ref">史記·《殷本紀》 5</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>「百姓不親，五品不訓，汝為司徒而敬敷五教，五教在寬。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The people are wanting in affection for one another, and do not observe the five orders of relationship.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
