      <prop type="x-translation-ref">史記·《殷本紀》 6</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>」封于商，賜姓子氏。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>You, as Minister of Instruction, should reverently inculcate the lessons of duty belonging to those five orders, but do so with gentleness.</seg>
      </tuv>
